text: David Theander (19 March 1892 - 18 July 1985) was a Swedish swimmer. He competed in the men's 400 metre freestyle event at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1892 births Category:1985 deaths Category:Swedish male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Sweden Category:Swimmers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm Category:Male freestyle swimmers
